{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "9f615580-6041-48d6-b8b6-a84ccfa9b4ab",
    "name": "Rental PS API",
    "description": "API untuk sistem manajemen rental PlayStation. Collection ini mencakup health check, auth/login, console, product, package, transaction flow utama, dan admin API.\n\nJalankan server dulu:\n- npm start\n- atau\n- npm run dev\n\nUrutan test manual yang disarankan:\n1. Health Check\n2. Login\n3. List Consoles\n4. List Products\n5. List Packages\n6. List Active Transactions\n7. Start Open Transaction\n8. Add Item to Transaction\n9. Finish Transaction\n10. Start Package Transaction\n11. Move Console\n12. Finish Package Transaction\n13. Admin - Create Product\n14. Admin - Update Product\n15. Admin - Create Cashier\n16. Admin - Set Console Maintenance\n\nCatatan penting:\n- Collection ini mengubah data database.\n- Stok produk akan berkurang.\n- Status console akan berubah sementara.\n- Transaction baru akan tercatat.\n- Request admin juga dapat membuat master data baru atau menonaktifkan data lama.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
